name: Extensive Anaerobic 50sec #2
description:
With repeated anaerobic bouts of 50sec, you will be improving your ability to process lactate and recover from strenuous efforts. With ample recovery between intervals today, you should be hitting each effort fresh and ready to go. 



Start the interval out of the seat before sitting and finding your rhythm for the remainder of the effort.
